name: Unidentified_Devaronian_Jedi
content: A Devaronian female Jedi served the Jedi Order during the High Republic Era. Around 231 BBY, the Jedi was present in the entryway of the Jedi Temple on Coruscant when Jedi Master Cohmac Vitus and Jedi Knight Vernestra Rwoh arrived, both having been summoned to Coruscant after lengthy periods away. When Vitus and Rwoh noticed a large tapestry decorating the hall, the Devaronian approached them, welcoming them back to the Temple and commenting on the tapestry's depiction of a battle between Jedi and Sith. At Vitus' request, she filled them in on the history of the artwork, which had been made by the Jedi Sherche La Plenn and recovered by the Galactic Republic, which had returned the tapestry to the Jedi in thanks for their assistance during the previous year's Great Hyperspace Disaster. After Vitus thanked her for the information, she moved off to greet other visitors. She had fine white fur and walked with light steps.
